      "side": 1,
      "message": "That\u0027s a really good point, Ben. With your earlier comment about if the attribute should be String or not... should I keep it as a string and then try to parse out a number vs string here, in this class, or do you think it\u0027s worth making some kind of new attribute type that can resolve to either a string or a number? I\u0027m not exactly sure how that would work but I\u0027m open to suggestions.",
